{"tid":1081315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇完笑咗] 騰訊否認監測用戶　稱投放廣告與聊天內容相似屬巧合","createTime":"2019-03-28T08:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T08:36:33.000Z","uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b970914b9e8d670ff2d4a2395047794432550c93","tid":1081315,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>騰訊否認監測用戶　稱投放廣告與聊天內容相似屬巧合</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時通訊軟件微信，否認監測用戶聊天記錄，亦不會通過監測數據向用戶發送廣告。<br />\n<br />\n軟件的開發商騰訊，回應内地傳媒時表示，用戶聊天記錄屬於個人私隱，不會進行監測。騰訊表示，廣告客戶可以選擇投放廣告給設定的目標人群。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊解釋，廣告投放的人群非常廣，很容易出現用戶收到的廣告，恰好與自己的聊天内容、瀏覽内容相似的巧合情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450128-20190328.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450128-20190328.htm&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AN7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=8ffe3e00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1450128-20190328.htm&h=84a73f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1450128-20190328.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n無監測？廣告純屬巧合？當人白癡咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62ec0fe3999a607f5b4114e395da9041be4cfb3","tid":1081315,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"我話巧合就巧合啦<br />\n唔通樣樣同你解釋咩"},{"pid":"18919648670006a0990dd2a492c156c612dbc9f4","tid":1081315,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62ec0fe3999a607f5b4114e395da9041be4cfb3","tid":1081315,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"我話巧合就巧合啦<br />\n唔通樣樣同你解釋咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"以後喺 QQ 講習帝壞話俾支共拉咗，可以話用戶俾人拉純屬巧合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8490dafc6cf7a2a3daf80ec65a199069ada90e7f","tid":1081315,"uid":4